  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 52.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gunther, can you tell me more about camp?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Describe it a little bit, the conditions of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The odor was unbelievable because everything was open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The reason why they were elevated is that they had a system of trains that came around the camp run by inmates who would empty these buckets every day and bring new ones.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other thing that I remember well is there was no hot water, everything was cold water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to wash with cold water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were hours when you could or could not go to wash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were certain areas where there were open air basins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Pyrenees can get very cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where we had to wash ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Laundry had to be washed there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They gave you certain hours when you could do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the camp, each-- each [INAUDIBLE] had its own basic administration, which was more or less inmate run.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A woman was chief of the [INAUDIBLE], they had their own kitchen and women were doing the cooking.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had a doctor in each [INAUDIBLE] in a hospital barracks and he would treat whoever needed help.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The biggest problem was dysentery, and it was deadly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One of the things that comes to mind most vividly was when we got there, there were mounds in the middle of the [INAUDIBLE], about, oh, three to four feet tall, made of dirt.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And no one ever could figure out why these mounds were there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then when it started to rain, we suddenly realized what they were because as the dirt washed away, arms and legs came out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "These were Spanish prisoners who had died and they had made underground graves for them, mass graves, and just covered them with dirt.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
